channel.description:
I want to add some commands in my 525, could someone post a tut and snippers please?
For moderators+ ::hide (this will hide someone and when he talks the text only come in the chatbox, like matrix) ::unhide (become normal again)
For admins+ ::kill (username) (kills username) ::killall (kills all username) ::noclip (let admins noclip) ::god (make 35k hp and 1-9k hits)
Maybe it takes a long job to make this, but who will make this gets a reward of 40$ (YOU MUST BE PAYPAL)
